text: Stina Haage (3 August 1924 - 15 June 2017)Stina Haage's profile at the Swedish Olympic Committee was a Swedish gymnast who competed in the 1948 Summer Olympics, in London. ==References== Category:1924 births Category:2017 deaths Category:Swedish female artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Sweden Category:Gymnasts at the 1948 Summer Olympics
